12
00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:01.913
- Trying to make up...
- [man] This is it?

13
00:01:01.937 --> 00:01:03.144
Hey. yeah. Come in.

14
00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:06.689
You guys made me ask off
an hour early to see this dump?

15
00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:10.505
