28
00:01:36.763 --> 00:01:38.254
<i>When</i>. When you have a baby.

29
00:01:38.348 --> 00:01:41.056
We're having a baby. We <i>are</i> having a baby.

30
00:01:41.143 --> 00:01:43.681
You see that? That's called
