127
00:06:13.498 --> 00:06:15.455
Hey. you want to watch
a little <i>Fixer Upper</i>?

128
00:06:17.085 --> 00:06:19.122
- Okay. I love you.
- I love you.

129
00:06:20.547 --> 00:06:21.913
