<i>That's a long fill-up. my friend.</i>

132
00:06:24.342 --> 00:06:26.404
[man] <i>Well. that's because I wanted you
to come in here.</i>

133
00:06:26.428 --> 00:06:28.948
<i>We're gonna have a karate kicking contest.
Me versus you. straight up.</i>

134
00:06:28.972 --> 00:06:29.972
